column5: Man, I hope he's got a carbide tip on the end of that thing, ptherwise things could get dull and bent pretty quick...
I wonder how long it took for him to figure it out...
Moose are very powerful animals, my money says he makes his own hole!!
Typical male, always putting women on a pedestal.
That would be all the hint I needed to leave the area!
From what I found out the statue had been shifted ahead about 6 inches...
